headline: ACN Q3 Earnings & Revenues Beat on Segmental Improvement, Rise Y/Y
summary: Accenture tops third-quarter fiscal 2025 estimates with 11.5% EPS growth and a 7.7% revenue gain, yet shares dip 3.7% post-earnings.

headline: L'ORÉAL PARIS DOCUMENTARY WINS GRAND PRIX IN FILM AT CANNES LIONS 2025
summary: "THE FINAL COPY OF ILON SPECHT," an emotional and cinematic tribute to the woman behind one of advertising's most enduring taglines, has won the Grand Prix in the Film category at the 2025 Cannes Lions International Festival of Creativity.
